    <lb n="14"/>λείας τῆς π<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">όλ</unclear>εως πράττειν, ἄχ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ρ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear>ς οὗ δ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ό</supplied>ξῃ τι τοῖς <choice><corr>μείζοσιν</corr><sic>μιζοσιν</sic></choice> περὶ τῆς ἡμετέρας 

